Power Rangers Dino Charge: Resurgence (DVD + Digital) does meet my expectations. The video, audio, and English subtitles work great. I really recommend this DVD to Power Ranger fans. I have been a fan of Power Rangers since Mighty Morphin Power Rangers came out in the early 90's. I am pleased with my purchase.

This is the second volume in the Dino Charge series.  It has four episodes: Breaking Black, The Tooth Hurts, Let Sleeping Zords Lie and Double Ranger, Double Danger.  The rangers have to fight monsters but also they have to learn to work as a team and that each person makes up the team.  The rangers have to deal with Chase being put under a spell and finding a way to break it, learning that teeth are important to their health, they find a new zord and even have clones of themselves that try to trick the Red Ranger.
Boring!
On Christmas morning my grandson watched it.  He loves the Power Rangers.
Excellent product!  Grandson loves it!!
